node.text: A few months ago, I met Ms. Lewis-Knight who is a teacher at a public school in Brooklyn. She told me about some of the challenges her students were facing with remote learning. The city can be a loud distracting place. But thanks to @amazon #deliveringsmiles, the students at PS40 will be receiving 400 headsets to help them focus better on their studies at home. Thank you Amazon!
